  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2407200/extras/fb996c4e34f5374eaffef05ce06722c9.poster.avif?t=1750429336\" width=600 height=116 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2407200/extras/fb996c4e34f5374eaffef05ce06722c9.webm?t=1750429336\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2407200/extras/fb996c4e34f5374eaffef05ce06722c9.mp4?t=1750429336\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>OVERWHELMED is a dynamic Twin Stick Shooter that immerses players in a minimalistic and neon atmosphere. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2407200/extras/47fb770e1b5c7f2dcf69f66e3184b93f.poster.avif?t=1750429336\" width=600 height=116 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2407200/extras/47fb770e1b5c7f2dcf69f66e3184b93f.webm?t=1750429336\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2407200/extras/47fb770e1b5c7f2dcf69f66e3184b93f.mp4?t=1750429336\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Take control of a spaceship and face waves of enemies, from small drones to fearsome bosses, using your shooting and dashing skills to evade enemy fire.<br><br>As you progress, you'll earn rewards to upgrade your spaceship's features and purchase new characters to face the 6 terrible bosses standing in your way.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2407200/extras/99a38fe796869be58cca7af5fe6070f2.poster.avif?t=1750429336\" width=600 height=116 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2407200/extras/99a38fe796869be58cca7af5fe6070f2.webm?t=1750429336\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2407200/extras/99a38fe796869be58cca7af5fe6070f2.mp4?t=1750429336\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>OVERWHELMED also introduces a special feature: the \"Overheat\". <br><br>A gauge fills up as you shoot, until it reaches 100%.<br><br>At that moment, you can no longer shoot, but you trigger your spaceship's special ability, allowing you to easily defeat waves of enemies for a limited time.<br><br>Use this ability wisely to overcome all obstacles!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2407200/extras/b3552bece7b6ac2eb0a3d4bba2923777.poster.avif?t=1750429336\" width=600 height=116 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2407200/extras/b3552bece7b6ac2eb0a3d4bba2923777.webm?t=1750429336\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2407200/extras/b3552bece7b6ac2eb0a3d4bba2923777.mp4?t=1750429336\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>OVERWHELMED features 6 playable characters, each with their own \"Overheat\" ability, music, and weapons.<br>Discover the unique gameplay style of each character and find the one that best suits your playstyle!<br>You'll have a varied arsenal to defeat enemies!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2407200/extras/e0a0fc21175dfac85222650adc8297a1.poster.avif?t=1750429336\" width=600 height=116 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2407200/extras/e0a0fc21175dfac85222650adc8297a1.webm?t=1750429336\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2407200/extras/e0a0fc21175dfac85222650adc8297a1.mp4?t=1750429336\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>With its fast gameplay, catchy music, and immersive neon atmosphere, OVERWHELMED offers an addictive and challenging gaming experience you won't forget anytime soon. <br>Get ready to face the challenges ahead and become the master of OVERWHELMED!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> The Overheat : Shooting increases the overheat value. When it reaches 100%, it unleashes an ability that damages enemies on contact, but disables the player's shooting.<br></li><li> Minimalist neon aesthetic<br></li><li> 10+ skills to unlock<br></li><li> 5 challenging bosses<br></li><li> 6 spaceships with their own gameplay</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2407200/extras/fb996c4e34f5374eaffef05ce06722c9.poster.avif?t=1750429336\" width=600 height=116 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2407200/extras/fb996c4e34f5374eaffef05ce06722c9.webm?t=1750429336\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2407200/extras/fb996c4e34f5374eaffef05ce06722c9.mp4?t=1750429336\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>OVERWHELMED is a dynamic Twin Stick Shooter that immerses players in a minimalistic and neon atmosphere. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2407200/extras/47fb770e1b5c7f2dcf69f66e3184b93f.poster.avif?t=1750429336\" width=600 height=116 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2407200/extras/47fb770e1b5c7f2dcf69f66e3184b93f.webm?t=1750429336\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2407200/extras/47fb770e1b5c7f2dcf69f66e3184b93f.mp4?t=1750429336\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Take control of a spaceship and face waves of enemies, from small drones to fearsome bosses, using your shooting and dashing skills to evade enemy fire.<br><br>As you progress, you'll earn rewards to upgrade your spaceship's features and purchase new characters to face the 6 terrible bosses standing in your way.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2407200/extras/99a38fe796869be58cca7af5fe6070f2.poster.avif?t=1750429336\" width=600 height=116 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2407200/extras/99a38fe796869be58cca7af5fe6070f2.webm?t=1750429336\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2407200/extras/99a38fe796869be58cca7af5fe6070f2.mp4?t=1750429336\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>OVERWHELMED also introduces a special feature: the \"Overheat\". <br><br>A gauge fills up as you shoot, until it reaches 100%.<br><br>At that moment, you can no longer shoot, but you trigger your spaceship's special ability, allowing you to easily defeat waves of enemies for a limited time.<br><br>Use this ability wisely to overcome all obstacles!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2407200/extras/b3552bece7b6ac2eb0a3d4bba2923777.poster.avif?t=1750429336\" width=600 height=116 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2407200/extras/b3552bece7b6ac2eb0a3d4bba2923777.webm?t=1750429336\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2407200/extras/b3552bece7b6ac2eb0a3d4bba2923777.mp4?t=1750429336\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>OVERWHELMED features 6 playable characters, each with their own \"Overheat\" ability, music, and weapons.<br>Discover the unique gameplay style of each character and find the one that best suits your playstyle!<br>You'll have a varied arsenal to defeat enemies!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2407200/extras/e0a0fc21175dfac85222650adc8297a1.poster.avif?t=1750429336\" width=600 height=116 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2407200/extras/e0a0fc21175dfac85222650adc8297a1.webm?t=1750429336\" type=\